text: Dimitar Galinchev (born 15 September 1938) is a Bulgarian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 63 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Bulgaria Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
